OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police find
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions on the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FPolice seizures of illegally modified
OL,8,Felectric bikes (e-bikes) soared in the
OL,9,Fpast year amid concerns their speed
OL,10,Fand weight present a lethal threat to
OL,11,Fpedestrians, an investigation has
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FForces across the UK confiscated 937 e-
OL,15,Fbikes in the year to August 11,
OL,16,Faccording to Freedom of Information
OL,17,F(FoI) figures.
OL,19,FThat is compared with 511 during the
OL,20,Fprevious 12 months.
