OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police find
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions on the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FUnder UK law, e-bike motors must cut
OL,8,Fout when a speed of 15.5mph is
OL,9,Freached, but police are finding many
OL,10,Fhave been modified to be much faster.
OL,12,FIt is also common for officers to find
OL,13,Fe-bikes that can be powered without
OL,14,Fthe pedals being turned, effectively
OL,15,Fmaking them electric mopeds or
OL,16,Fmotorbikes which must be registered
OL,17,Fand taxed.
OL,19,FConversion kits are available online
OL,20,Ffor as little as #300.
