OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police find
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions on the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FCity of London Police recently seized
OL,8,Fan e-bike capable of reaching 70mph,
OL,9,Fwhich featured an electronic display
OL,10,Findicating it had covered more than
OL,11,F6,000 miles.
OL,13,FDuring another operation outside
OL,14,FLondon Liverpool Street railway
OL,15,Fstation earlier this month, it took
OL,16,Fofficers just minutes to catch a rider
OL,17,Fusing an illegal e-bike.
