OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police find
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions on the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FThe e-bike had a motor with a maximum
OL,8,Fpower output was 500 watts - twice the
OL,9,Flegal limit -as well as severely worn
OL,10,Fout tyres and a bundle of loose
OL,11,Felectric wires stored in a soaking wet
OL,12,Fpouch.
OL,14,FAn officer at the scene described it
OL,15,Fas "a death trap", adding: "This could
OL,16,Feasily kill him or someone else."
OL,18,FNo action was taken against the rider
OL,19,F- a food delivery worker - but his e-
OL,20,Fbike was confiscated and will likely
OL,21,Fbe destroyed.
