OL,7,FSome forces said their figures related
OL,8,Fto all e-bike seizures, while others
OL,9,Fspecified their statistics were for
OL,10,Fillegal e-bikes.
OL,12,FThe overall 83% rise in e-bike
OL,13,Fconfiscations suggested by the
OL,14,Finvestigation underplays the true
OL,15,Fscale of the surge, as some forces did
OL,16,Fnot provide comparable figures.
